author: David
title: David
text: If you're confused or having a hard time finding a reliable seafood supermarket, this is the one! They promote environment health all the way & most sustainable fishing practices! They are the BEST for the price when you buy in bulk! You can always guarantee no matter what product you're getting TOP QUALITY! I tried ordering seafood from other vendors & websites & also even tried trying wild caught Alaskan Salmon in restaurants & still this is the best one yet. GOOD LUCK if you can find BETTER! Vital Choice is PRIME!
